OL,3,CMarco Rubio arrives in UAE to ease
OL,4,CGulf states' scepticism over Iran deal
OL,6,FUS Secretary of State Marco Rubio is
OL,7,Fin the United Arab Emirates on the
OL,8,Ffirst leg of a three-nation tour of
OL,9,FGulf countries aimed at easing their
OL,10,Fconcerns about the result of an
OL,11,Fagreement intended to end the war with
OL,12,FIran.
OL,14,FRubio arrived in Abu Dhabi late on
OL,15,FTuesday following a two-day flurry of
OL,16,Fdiplomatic activity between the US and
OL,17,FIran in Switzerland led by Vice
OL,18,FPresident JD Vance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
