CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782312494
OL,3,CMarco Rubio arrives in UAE to ease
OL,4,CGulf states' scepticism over Iran deal
OL,6,FThis resulted in what Vance called a
OL,7,Fsignificant agreement to end all
OL,8,Fhostilities in the region, reopen the
OL,9,FStrait of Hormuz and provide sanctions
OL,10,Frelief with negotiations on its
OL,11,Fnuclear program to be concluded in 60
OL,12,Fdays.
OL,14,FIn the UAE, Kuwait and Bahrain ` all
OL,15,Fnations that Iran hit with missiles
OL,16,Fand drones in retaliation for US-
OL,17,FIsraeli airstrikes ` Rubio will be
OL,18,Fholding meetings starting Wednesday
OL,19,Fwith leaders who, in some cases, have
OL,20,Ftaken a harder line on Iran recently
OL,21,Fthan has the Trump administration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
