OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782312494
OL,3,CMarco Rubio arrives in UAE to ease
OL,4,CGulf states' scepticism over Iran deal
OL,6,FSpeaking to reporters upon his
OL,7,Farrival, Rubio said he would explain
OL,8,Fthe benefits of the agreement to the
OL,9,Fsceptical Gulf states if it is
OL,10,Fimplemented.
OL,12,FHe said that a proposed $300 billion
OL,13,F(#227 million) investment fund for
OL,14,FIran would not become a reality unless
OL,15,F"its leadership makes a decision that
OL,16,Fthey want to be a country instead of a
OL,17,Frevolutionary movement that exports
OL,18,Fterror".
OL,26,@zD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
