OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782312494
OL,3,CMarco Rubio arrives in UAE to ease
OL,4,CGulf states' scepticism over Iran deal
OL,6,FAnother complaint is that the
OL,7,Fagreement does not cover Iran's
OL,8,Fmissile program, its support for
OL,9,Fproxies and pushes off the nuclear
OL,10,Fquestion until later.
OL,12,FRubio argued, however, that the
OL,13,Fmemorandum of understanding signed
OL,14,Flast week calls for the "complete end
OL,15,Fof hostilities and conflicts in the
OL,16,Fregion," which he said will require
OL,17,FIran to halt its funding of proxies
OL,18,Flike Hamas in Gaza, Hezbollah in
OL,19,FLebanon and the Houthis in Yemen.
OL,26,@vD@YOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782312494
OL,3,CMarco Rubio arrives in UAE to ease
OL,4,CGulf states' scepticism over Iran deal
OL,6,F"You can't have the end of hostilities
OL,7,Fand conflicts in a region as long as
OL,8,FIranian proxies are launching missiles
OL,9,Fand drones from Iraq, and are
OL,10,Fparticipating in terrorism, like Hamas
OL,11,Fdid, and like Hezbollah did," Rubio
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"So, I do think it's covered by the
OL,15,FMOU, and it is an issue that will be
OL,16,Fgotten to at the appropriate time in
OL,17,Fthese negotiations."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@]O]vD@AOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
