OL,3,CMarco Rubio arrives in UAE to ease
OL,4,CGulf states' scepticism over Iran deal
OL,6,FThe Emiratis, in particular, have been
OL,7,Fat the forefront of calls for tough
OL,8,Faction notably to ensure the reopening
OL,9,Fof the Strait of Hormuz ` a critical
OL,10,Fwaterway through which around a fifth
OL,11,Fof the world's oil and gas passes
OL,12,Fbefore the war.
OL,14,FThere have been conflicting accounts
OL,15,Fof what the Memorandum of
OL,16,FUnderstanding signed last week will
OL,17,Fmean for the strait, which the rest of
OL,18,Fthe world wants open free of charge
OL,19,Ffor all shipping.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782312494
OL,3,CMarco Rubio arrives in UAE to ease
OL,4,CGulf states' scepticism over Iran deal
OL,6,FThe US has been firm on that point,
OL,7,Fbut the Iranians are moving ahead with
OL,8,Fa scheme that could charge service
OL,9,Ffees for passage that many believe
OL,10,Fwould amount to a toll.
OL,12,FInsisting that under no circumstances
OL,13,Fwould the US accept that, Rubio said:
OL,14,F"It's an international waterway... No
OL,15,Fcountry is allowed to charge tolls or
OL,16,Ffees on an international waterway.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
