OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782312494
OL,3,CMarco Rubio arrives in UAE to ease
OL,4,CGulf states' scepticism over Iran deal
OL,6,F"That's existing international law.
OL,7,FThat's the way it is. I don't think we
OL,8,Fhave anybody to convince around here
OL,9,Fin that regard. I think all the
OL,10,Fcountries in this region would agree
OL,11,Fwith us."
